channel.title: Cooking Issue
channel.description:
Well, on my server say you have one raw lobbie. You use on range. you then right click the image of your fish, and hit cook 'x'. You can type any number in here even though you only have 1 raw fish, and it will still cook that many.
http://pastebin.com/dh9eGqbt
those are my cooking voids. whoever helps, can collect a reward!
